=Resources=

From Smári McCarthy:

Currently there are a few ways to do this:
  
- For simpler T-shirt designs, etc, Cafepress (http://www.cafepress.com/) does a wonderful job.
  
- For more complicated textile designs, [[Burdastyle]] (http://www.burdastyle.com/) is a great source of open source sewing, etc.
  
- Threadless takes Burdastyle into the marketplace: http://www.threadless.com


More general resources:

- Instructables (http://www.instructables.com)
  
- Make Magazine's Maker Faire (http://www.makezine.com)
  
- Etsy (http://www.etsy.com)
  

